Adam Matthew Explorer

Database available to authorized IU Bloomington users (on or off campus)

Alias URL: amexplorer

Allows users to search all Adam Matthew digital collections.

Coverage: Varies

Vendor: Adam Matthew

Producer: Adam Matthew
